<p>The script redirects users to non secure site.</p>
<p>Plugin default settings:</p>
<ul class="list-unstyled">
   <li>"displayModal": true</li>
   <li>"exitMsg": "You are about to leave a secure site, do you wish to continue?"</li>
   <li>"cancelMsg": "Annuler"</li>
   <li>"yesMsg": "Oui"</li>
   <li>“targetBlank”:  target _self</li>
</ul>
<p>Test the plugin: <a href="http://csszengarden.com/219" class="wb-exitscript" data-wb-exitscript='{"exitURL": "http://www.canada.ca"}'>http://csszengarden.com/219</a></p>
